<template><div><h1 id="fast-glob" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#fast-glob" aria-hidden="true">#</a> fast-glob</h1>
<blockquote>
<p>It's a very fast and efficient <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glob_(programming)" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">glob<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> library for <a href="https://nodejs.org/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Node.js<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This package provides methods for traversing the file system and returning pathnames that matched a defined set of a specified pattern according to the rules used by the Unix Bash shell with some simplifications, meanwhile results are returned in <strong>arbitrary order</strong>. Quick, simple, effective.</p>
